Also their maintainer says they probably won't ever use it: http://stackoverflow.com/questions/24844901/bowers-bower-json-file-version-property

Update bower.json

need to add "main" property to bower.json or build systems will not know which file to include

adding "main" property to point to "./humane.min.js" will point to correct file to use for general production use!

Merge pull request #27 from JensRoland/master

Queued notification overwrites previous

Fix issue #26: Queued notification overwrites previous

Since the defaults object is being passed by reference rather than
cloned, every queued notification will share the same html, options and
callback. This commit creates a shallow clone instead
